lead_paragraph: A second-string South Africa side drew 31-31 with the Barbarians in an exciting try fest at Wembley on Saturday that served as a warm-up for the Springboks' test against England next weekend.

headline.print_headline: South Africa Draw With Barbarians at Start of European Tour
